        <div aria-labelledby="diversity-equity-inclusion-button" class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel" data-tab-panel="diversity-equity-inclusion-panel" id="diversity-equity-inclusion-panel" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
         <span class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-title">
          Diversity, equity &amp; inclusion
         </span>
         <div class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-body">
          <p>
           We are all-in to promote an inclusive, accessible campus and advocate for our students and community. We do this by asking tough, student-centered questions and then consistently working to improve, through
           <a href="https://diversity.iupui.edu/initiatives/anti-racism-initiatives/index.html">
            anti-racism initiatives
           </a>
           , by
           <a href="https://diversity.iupui.edu/land-acknowledgment/index.html">
            honoring the heritage of Native peoples
           </a>
           , and more.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div aria-labelledby="student-success-button" class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel" data-tab-panel="student-success-panel" hidden="" id="student-success-panel" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
         <span class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-title">
          Student success
         </span>
         <div class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-body">
          <p>
           We promote student learning and success in everything we do. Our students are our partners as we focus on their personal and professional development. Our location in Indianapolis provides valuable opportunities our students can only get here.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div aria-labelledby="educational-excellence-button" class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel" data-tab-panel="educational-excellence-panel" hidden="" id="educational-excellence-panel" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
         <span class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-title">
          Educational excellence
         </span>
         <div class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-body">
          <p>
           We set high standards for our faculty and staff, so we invest in them. They return advancements in health and life sciences and accelerate innovation and discovery through research and creative activity. All the while, they provide excellence in teaching, scholarship, and service to our students.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div aria-labelledby="community-engagement-button" class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel" data-tab-panel="community-engagement-panel" hidden="" id="community-engagement-panel" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
         <span class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-title">
          Community engagement
         </span>
         <div class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel-body">
          <p>
           We’re committed to strengthening the bond we have forged with our community. As a leader in fostering collaborative relationships, we strive to make consistent intellectual, economic, and cultural contributions through community partnerships.
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div aria-labelledby="safety-button" class="rvt-c-hybrid-tabs__panel" data-tab-panel="safety-panel" hidden="" id="safety-panel" role="tabpanel" tabindex="0">
